  "body": "<!--NOTE: -->\r\n<!--- General questions should go to the discord chat instead of the issue tracker.-->\r\n\r\n**Describe the bug**\r\n\r\nBeacon API code includes regen code that's very sensitive in terms of performance and memory.\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/blob/aba0815ee5b6571c882335717bdf2aa304e3c193/packages/lodestar/src/api/impl/beacon/state/utils.ts#L269-L277\r\n\r\nThis code should be moved into regen and unified there to ensure the caches and its usage is consistent and safe.\r\n\r\n",
